   侠客行游戏的命令分为下列几类：

   [44;1m[1;33m〔玩家命令〕                                                                  [37;0m
   alias    board      clear      chat     color     describe   finger   help     
   hp       id         inventory  locate   mudlist   nick       passwd   quit     
   rumor    save       score      set      suicide   time       title    to
   unset    uptime     version    vote     wenxuan   who        wimpy    wizlist  

   [44;1m[1;33m〔探险命令〕                                                                  [37;0m
   ask      beg        block      boss      buy      check      close    drop     
   emote    feed       fight      follow    get      give       go       halt     
   hit      jingzuo    kill       lead      look     marry      open     persuade   
   propose  put        ride       remove    reply    say        semote   shout    
   sleep    steal      tell       throw     train    trap       tune     unride    
   unwield  vote       wear       whisper   wield    yin

   [44;1m[1;33m〔武功命令〕                                                                  [37;0m
   abandon(fangqi)    apprentice(bai)       enable(jifa)        enforce(jiali)
   exercise(dazuo)    exert(yun)            expell(kaichu)      learn(xue)      
   respirate(tuna)    perform(yong)         practice(lian)      recruit(shou)
   skills(cha)        study(du)             prepare(bei)        enpower(jiajing)
